  "body": "spike to determine the level of effort to support flashbots v0.3 RPC and/or eden:\n  https://docs.flashbots.net/flashbots-auction/miners/mev-geth-spec/v03\n\n* determine impacts on PGA transaction selection\n* LoE to manage and incorporate bundle pool\n  * bundle validation and selection\n* LoE to support bundle simulation\n* considerations about endpoint security, mev-relay\n\nresources:\nhttps://docs.flashbots.net/\n\nhttps://docs.edennetwork.io/\nhttps://edennetwork.io/EDEN_Network___Whitepaper___2021_07.pdf",
